### Create entry
POST {{baseUrl}}/entries
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "entry": "Yesterday was a productive day.",
  "location": "Kyiv"
}

### Get entry
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/{{entry_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List entries by user
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search entries
POST {{baseUrl}}/entries/search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "query": "productive day"
}

### Get summary (30-day default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get summary (7-day)
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/summary?period=7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get narrative (current week, default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/narrative
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get narrative (current month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/narrative?type=month
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get narrative (specific week)
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/narrative?type=week&key=2026-W21
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get narrative (force refresh)
GET {{baseUrl}}/entries/narrative?type=week&refresh=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}